{
  "stem": "23428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think they were divorced at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So officially, he had to have another residence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, after his-- I think were his protectors until that day vanished after July 20th, 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some SS men apparently came to the hotel, forced him to-- to hand over the gold, and arrested him.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then-- OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So two weeks later or so, I was in Pest for something, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Came home, nobody was at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean my mother, my brother were not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It turns out they had been picked up by SS men in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I sat around the apartment a little bit, stupid kid that I was, totally unable to understand at the time, and really just waited until they picked me up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we ended up, all four of us, in the main Gestapo prison in Hungary, that is located at Fo Utca, of which I also have taken numerous photographs if you want to see it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It still exists and has become very famous, because at that time already it housed the Hungarian government of that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And later it was a place where Nagy was executed by the Communists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It also became later the main Communist detention center for Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The street Fo Utca, F-O-- O umlaut, yeah, F-O umlaut, Utca street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like [HUNGARIAN.]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since wealth-- yeah, of course not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since-- since-- since I think since the gold days we bought a marvelous apartment in the elegant part of the city, in Buda, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on what was then called [HUNGARIAN] 55.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now it's called [HUNGARIAN], very nice area.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
